itemLabel: John Godfrey Huggins, 2nd Viscount Malvern of Rhodesia and Bexley
itemDescription: (1922-1978), Son of 1st Viscount Malvern of Rhodesia

wikipedia_page.main: John Godfrey Huggins, 2nd Viscount Malvern of Rhodesia and of Bexley (26 October 1922 - 28 August 1978) was a British peer and officer in the Royal Air Force during the Second World War.
